OL,3,C'Chopstick Sally' allows housebound
OL,4,Cauthor to feel more included in society
OL,6,F"I went from working full-time,
OL,7,Fexercising and socialising to being
OL,8,Fhousebound and largely bedbound.
OL,10,F"I have a huge array of symptoms such
OL,11,Fas physical fatigue, cognitive fatigue
OL,12,F` often described as brain fog, muscle
OL,13,Faches, insomnia, lightheadedness,
OL,14,Fnausea."
OL,16,FShe has to spend prolonged periods of
OL,17,Ftime in bed resting interspersed with
OL,18,Fessential tasks including eating and
OL,19,Fshowering, as well as writing.
