OL,3,C'Chopstick Sally' allows housebound
OL,4,Cauthor to feel more included in society
OL,6,FIn a bid to spread the word about her
OL,7,Fbooks and explore the country, she
OL,8,Fcame up with the idea of creating a
OL,9,Fminiature version of herself which
OL,10,Fwould feature on chopsticks and go to
OL,11,Fevents in place of her ` and so,
OL,12,FChopstick Sally was born.
OL,14,F"In March this year, my second book,
OL,15,FToby and the Wizards of Wildhaven, was
OL,16,Fshortlisted for an award and I was
OL,17,Finvited to a ceremony at London Book
OL,18,FFair," she said.
