OL,4,Cauthor to feel more included in society
OL,6,F"I was gutted that I couldn't go and
OL,7,Fso this gave me the motivation to
OL,8,Fcreate Chopstick Sally."
OL,10,FTo create Chopstick Sally, Ms Doherty
OL,11,Fposes for photos in different outfits
OL,12,Fwhich her husband takes.
OL,14,FThey are uploaded to a laptop, printed
OL,15,Foff, cut and stuck to cardboard and
OL,16,Fthen chopsticks.
OL,18,F"Chopstick Sally has had three
OL,19,Fdifferent outfits so far and I think
OL,20,Fshe'll need another change of outfit
OL,21,Fsoon," she added.
