OL,6,FThe outfits include a black dress with
OL,7,Fwhite polka dots and a pink wrap dress.
OL,9,FSo far, Chopstick Sally has been to
OL,10,Fevents including Ms Doherty's cousin's
OL,11,Fwedding, a hen-do, the HarperCollins
OL,12,Fauthor party for Ms Doherty's new book
OL,13,F` Max and Monty: The Raven Thief ` and
OL,14,Fa book awards ceremony at The London
OL,15,FBook Fair.
