OL,6,FAuthor Lindsay Galvin took Chopstick
OL,7,FSally to the HarperCollins author
OL,8,Fparty while bookseller Helen Tamblyn-
OL,9,FSaville gave the mini cutout a tour of
OL,10,Fher bookshop ` Wonderland Bookshop, in
OL,11,FRetford.
OL,13,F"(Helen Tamblyn-Saville) went out of
OL,14,Fher way to make me feel involved and
OL,15,Fshared lots of pictures of Chopstick
OL,16,FSally in the shop," Ms Doherty said.
OL,18,F"This was the first time ever that I
OL,19,Fgot to be photographed against my
OL,20,Ffirst book (Toby and the Silver Blood
OL,21,FWitches) on a bookshop shelf.
