OL,3,C'Chopstick Sally' allows housebound
OL,4,Cauthor to feel more included in society
OL,6,F"(She) even took (Chopstick Sally) to
OL,7,Fa booksellers' conference where I got
OL,8,Fto meet Rick Astley."
OL,10,FMs Doherty said she often asks loved
OL,11,Fones if they can take her cardboard
OL,12,Falter-ego to events and some people on
OL,13,Fsocial media have even offered to do
OL,14,Fit.
OL,16,F"It's been lovely to see how much
OL,17,Fpeople have supported it," she said.
