OL,3,C'Chopstick Sally' allows housebound
OL,4,Cauthor to feel more included in society
OL,6,F"When you become housebound, you
OL,7,Fliterally disappear from society ` and
OL,8,Fit's easy for people to forget about
OL,9,Fyou if they don't see you ` which is
OL,10,Fweird as you're still living, albeit
OL,11,Fin a reduced capacity.
OL,13,F"So this is a great way of making me
OL,14,Ffeel more included ` and reminding
OL,15,Fpeople that I exist too.
OL,17,F"Obviously, it'll never make up for
OL,18,Fattending events in person, but it's
OL,19,Fbetter than nothing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU{D@UO]
