OL,6,FShe said she has received messages
OL,7,Ffrom people who either have an illness
OL,8,For know others who do who have enjoyed
OL,9,Finteracting with Chopstick Sally.
OL,11,F"I was recently contacted by someone
OL,12,Fwho had seen Chopstick Sally on X,"
OL,13,Fshe said.
OL,15,F"Their best friend has long Covid and
OL,16,Fthey were planning to create a
OL,17,Fcardboard/chopstick version of them to
OL,18,Ftake on holiday as a surprise. I'm
OL,19,Fsure their friend will absolutely love
OL,20,Fit.
